香港仲係win"},{"pid":"dcd356a977f31a6a7037d2d7b956e79af2ba4450","tid":197390,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本係幾好既 我都幾鍾意<br />\n但我覺得好多國家都唔錯<br />\n紐澳北歐埃及都好好<br />\n想睇景近近地又可以返大陸<br />\n張家界九寨溝桂林都冇得輸</blockquote><br />\n景係靚  但係人患係最大問題<br />\n日本好就好在人多時啲人(日本人)仲係好有秩序   你唔駛成日驚哩樣煩個樣  雖然野食講煮法手功我覺得香港仲係win</blockquote><br />\n大陸真係人同食物既問題最大<br />\n人又嘈又冇秩序<br />\n食物又地溝油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇你敢唔敢豁出去咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好處係消費平同近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c44b3decbed3fa1ea60508e7c5ed7949a958889","tid":197390,"uid":90025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:07:13.000Z","msg":"香港好撚貴，完。"},{"pid":"e9552fbba20ef5ae65445dca4bf5f62f15836eee","tid":197390,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"崇泡喎而家 你活係咩年代"},{"pid":"9afd768f55d5cfffa6b3db2c6771c3652bf57cd9","tid":197390,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"香港真係多好多野食<br />\n<br />\n雖然個邊都有d香港食唔到既(吉列豬排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但係點都無岩香港人口味 (太多配菜同份量少)"},{"pid":"4e61376d7cbfaa62277fee5a1c458112d31426ec","tid":197390,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>崇泡喎而家 你活係咩年代</blockquote><br />\n仲係好崇日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}